Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:21.66,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,This is a simple thing to do if you understand the method.{やり方さえ分かっちゃえば簡単なもんだね}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.08,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,With this, I don't feel like I'll lose.{これなら負ける気がしないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:43.52,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'll give it to you.{あげるよ}
