Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.08,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan...{さやかちゃん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:16.55,Madoka,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't use that kind of fighting style.{あんな戦い方、ないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.77,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Saying that it isn't painful is a lie.{痛くないなんて嘘だよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.93,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Just watching you was painful.{見てるだけで痛かったもん}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:32.48,Madoka,,0,0,0,,You're fine getting injuries since you can't feel them...{感じないから傷ついてもいいなんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.81,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That sort of thing is no good!{そんなのダメだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.57,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I have to do that sort of thing or else I won't win.{ああでもしなきゃ勝てないんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.20,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Since I have no natural talent, you know.{あたし才能ないからさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.91,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If you fight with that kind of style, then even if you win,{あんなやり方で戦ってたら、勝てたとしても}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:48.12,Madoka,,0,0,0,,it won't be in your best interest, Sayaka-chan.{さやかちゃんのためにならないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.58,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,What is "in my best interest"?{あたしの為にって何よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:03.38,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,After I've been given this kind of form, what would you say is in my best interest?{こんな姿にされた後で、何が私の為になるって言うの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.14,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan...{さやかちゃん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:10.02,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You know, for me right now... Killing witches. I have no purpose except just that.{今の私はね、魔女を殺す、ただそれしかだけ意味がない}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:10.89,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'm a stone.{石ころなのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:15.61,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I only appear to be alive by moving a dead body.{死んだ身体を動かして生きてるフリをしてるだけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:19.61,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,For a thing such as my best interest, what would you say someone could do?{そんな私の為に、誰が何をしてくれるって言うの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:20.90,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Isn't it meaningless to even consider?{考えるだけ無意味じゃん}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:25.41,Madoka,,0,0,0,,But I... want to know how I can make you happy, Sayaka-chan.{でも私は…どうすればさやかちゃんが幸せになれるかって}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.99,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then you should fight.{だったらあんたが戦ってよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.46,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I heard it from Kyubey.{キュウべえから聞いたわよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:39.94,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You have more natural talent than anyone else, right?{あんた誰よりも才能あるんでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:43.76,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Without any of the hardships that someone like myself goes through, you could beat witches easily, right?{私みたいな苦労をしなくても簡単に魔女をやっつけられるんでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.18,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I...{私は}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.26,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That's...{そんな}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:53.77,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If you're saying you want to do something in my best interest, then start by trying to put yourself in the same position as me.{私の為に何かしようって言うんなら、まず私と同じ立場になってみなさいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.56,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Impossible, right? Of course it is.{無理でしょ。当然だよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:01.07,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't cease to be human merely out of sympathy, right?{ただの同情で人間やめらるわけないもんね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.82,Madoka,,0,0,0,,It isn't sympathy or anything! That's...{同情なんて…そんな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:10.45,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Although you could accomplish everything, you do nothing, and in your place I have to go through this experience.{何でも出来るくせに何もしないあんたの代わりに、あたしがこんな目に遭ってるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:13.58,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You put yourself on a pedestal and play innocent, so don't say things like "I understand."{それを棚に上げて、知ったような事言わないで}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.08,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan...{さやかちゃん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.09,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Don't come with me.{ついて来ないで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.56,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'm an idiot...{バカだよ私}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.65,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,What a thing to say...{何て事言ってんのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.69,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,There's no way to save me now...{もう救いようがないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:01.25,Homura,,0,0,0,,I predict that Walpurgis Night will appear within this range.{ワルプルギスの夜の出現予測は、この範囲}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:05.63,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,What's your basis?{根拠は何だい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.63,Homura,,0,0,0,,Statistics.{統計よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.63,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Statistics?{統計}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:13.47,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard of anything like a Walpurgis coming to this city before.{以前にもこの街にワルプルギスが来たなんて話は聞いてないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:16.23,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Really, just what exactly is the source of your statistics?{一体何をどう統計したってのさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:23.90,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Neither of us could be called anything like a trustworthy manga hero, but y'know...{お互い信用しろだなんていえる柄でもないけどさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.90,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be all right to show a bit more of the cards you hold?{もうちょっと手の内を見せてくれたっていいんじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.99,QB,,0,0,0,,That is something I, too, would certainly like to ask of you.{それはぜひ僕からもお願いしたいね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:30.99,QB,,0,0,0,,Akemi Homura.{暁美ほむら」}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.49,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Why are you showing your face around here? {\i1}You{\i0}...{どの面下げて出てきやがったテメェ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:38.33,QB,,0,0,0,,Well, well! Does that mean I'm an uninvited guest?{やれやれ、招かれざる客ってわけかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:43.79,QB,,0,0,0,,I came tonight to notify you of information that both of you will find important, though.{今夜は君たちにとって、重要なはずの情報を知らせに来たんだけどね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:44.63,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Hah?{はぁ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:47.97,QB,,0,0,0,,Miki Sayaka is exhausting herself faster than expected.{美樹さやかの消耗が予想以上に早い}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.84,QB,,0,0,0,,It isn't just her magical power usage.{魔力を使うだけでなく}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.80,QB,,0,0,0,,A curse has begun to form inside of her.{彼女自身が呪いを生み始めた}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.01,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Whose fault do you think that is, exactly?{誰のせいだと思ってんのさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:07:00.31,QB,,0,0,0,,If it continues at this rate, it may become troublesome before Walpurgis Night arrives.{このままだと、ワルプルギスの夜が来るより先に、厄介なことになるかもしれない}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:01.77,QB,,0,0,0,,You should act in a cautious manner.{注意しておいた方がいいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:05.02,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,What is that? What does that mean?{何だそりゃ。どういう意味だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:08.32,QB,,0,0,0,,Instead of me, what if you ask her?{僕じゃなくて、彼女に訊いてみたらどうだい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:12.16,QB,,0,0,0,,If it's you, then you should already know, right? Akemi Homura.{君なら既に知っているんじゃないかな？　暁美ほむら}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.45,QB,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.{やっぱりね}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:20.79,QB,,0,0,0,,Where did you obtain that information? I'm quite interested.{どこでその知識を手に入れたのか、僕はとても興味深い}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.33,QB,,0,0,0,,Are you...{君は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:24.46,Homura,,0,0,0,,I have heard what you want to ask.{聞くだけのことは聞いたわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:25.88,Homura,,0,0,0,,Vanish.{消えなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.56,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,You'll let that guy be?{ほっとくのかよアイツ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.64,Homura,,0,0,0,,Killing that thing won't result in any solution at all.{あれを殺したところで、何の解決にもならないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.77,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Miki Sayaka.{それよりも美樹さやかだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:45.15,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Just what is the "trouble" that guy was talking about?{アイツの言ってた厄介ごとってのは何なんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.90,Homura,,0,0,0,,Her Soul Gem has accumulated too much impurity.{彼女のソウルジェムは、穢れを溜め込み過ぎたのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:55.03,Homura,,0,0,0,,It must be purified quickly, or else it will result in an irrecoverable situation.{早く浄化しないと、取り返しのつかないことになる}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.00,0:08:06.09,Kazuko,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(600,0)}The auxiliary verb "must" means something that you are absolutely duty-bound to do.{"must"という助動詞には、これこれしなければならないといったような義務の意味があるのですが}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.63,Kazuko,,0,0,0,,{\an8}However, if it's "have to", then you're pushed...{"have to"だとどちらかとい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:13.51,Kazuko,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When you are expressing a general duty for one person, if "must" is used, it represents an individualistic sense of responsibility...{一一般的な義務を表す時があって、一方、"must"であれば個人的な責任感に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.97,Madoka,,0,0,0,,At that time... Even if chasing her was forbidden, I should have...{あの時…追いかけなきゃダメだったのに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:28.90,Kamijou Touma,,0,0,0,,But still, Shizuki-san, you return home in this direction?{でもさぁ、志筑さんって、帰る方角はこっちなんだっけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:33.28,Kamijou Touma,,0,0,0,,Up until now, it's like I haven't seen you return home this way...{今まで帰り道に見かけたことってないような…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.41,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,That's correct. It's actually in the completely opposite direction.{ええ。本当は全然逆方向ですわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.04,Kamijou Touma,,0,0,0,,Then... why today?{じゃあ、今日はどうして？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.17,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,Kamijou-kun,{上条君に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:48.00,Hitomi,,0,0,0,,I have something I'd like to say to you.{お話したいことがありますの}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.05,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Eh?{え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:54.68,Madoka,,0,0,0,,She hasn't come home? Since yesterday? That's...{帰ってないんですか。昨日から。その…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:58.35,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yes. Um... I understand.{はい。えっと、わかりました}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.26,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Yes.{はい}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.89,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.{失礼します}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.40,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sayaka-chan...{\i0}{さやかちゃん}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:15.91,Madoka,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to search for her.{\i0}{探さなきゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.59,Homura,,0,0,0,,Why don't you understand?{どうして分からないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:18.30,Homura,,0,0,0,,Since you simply lack the necessary surplus, aim only for witches.{ただでさえ余裕がないのだから、魔女だけを狙いなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.64,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Shut up.{うるさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:21.85,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the big, unnecessary help.{大きなお世話よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.10,Homura,,0,0,0,,Your Soul Gem is already at its limit.{もうソウルジェムも限界のはずよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.48,Homura,,0,0,0,,You must purify it immediately.{今すぐ浄化しないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.27,Homura,,0,0,0,,Use this.{使いなさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.49,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,What are you scheming this time?{今度は何を企んでるのさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:39.86,Homura,,0,0,0,,I have had enough.{いい加減にして}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:44.45,Homura,,0,0,0,,You're no longer in a situation where you can doubt people, are you?{もう人を疑ってる場合じゃないでしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:46.33,Homura,,0,0,0,,Do you find it that unpleasant to be given help?{そんなに助けられるのが嫌なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.33,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a different type of magical girl than all of you.{あんた達とは違う魔法少女になる}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.17,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That's what I decided.{私はそう決めたんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:59.34,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'd find it unpleasant to befriend those who would do something like abandon and use someone.{誰かを見捨てるのも、利用するのも、そんな事をする奴らとつるむのも嫌だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.22,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I don't need a reimbursement or anything.{見返りなんていらない}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:04.64,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who'll absolutely never use magic for her own benefit.{私だけは絶対に自分の為に魔法を使ったりしない}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.89,Homura,,0,0,0,,You... are going to die.{あなた、死ぬわよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:12.65,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If I were to die, it'd simply mean that my time to kill witches would be over.{あたしが死ぬとしたら、それは魔女を殺せなくなった時だけだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.02,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,In short, my use would come to an end.{それってつまり用済みって事じゃん}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.44,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That's fine, then.{ならいいんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:24.03,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,This world doesn't need someone like me if I can't beat witches.{魔女に勝てないあたしなんてこの世界にはいらないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.75,Homura,,0,0,0,,Hey, why?{ねえどうして}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:30.00,Homura,,0,0,0,,I only want to save you.{貴女を助けたいだけなの}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.50,Homura,,0,0,0,,Why won't you place your trust in me?{どうして信じてくれないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.88,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...{どうしてかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.80,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I simply understand, you know.{ただ何となく分かっちゃうんだよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.55,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That you are a liar.{あんたが嘘つきだって事}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:43.55,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Your eyes look like they've given up on anything and everything.{あんた、何もかも諦めた目をしてる}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.80,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You always speak empty words.{いつも空っぽな言葉を喋ってる}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:47.56,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That's even true right now.{今だってそう}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.31,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You say things like "It's for your benefit,"{あたしの為とか言いながら}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.81,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,but in truth you're thinking of something completely different, right?{ホントは全然別な事を考えてるんでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:55.02,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You can't completely deceive me. Not like that.{ごまかし切れるもんじゃないよ、そういうの}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:12:00.28,Homura,,0,0,0,,Just like that, you torment Madoka more and more.{そうやって、貴女はますますまどかを苦しめるのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.03,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Isn't Madoka unrelated?{まどかは関係ないでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:06.53,Homura,,0,0,0,,No. Anything and everything is for that girl's sake.{いいえ、何もかもあの子のためよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.34,Homura,,0,0,0,,You are sharp.{貴女って鋭いわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.71,Homura,,0,0,0,,Yes, you hit the mark.{ええ、図星よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.80,Homura,,0,0,0,,I don't want to help you.{私は貴女を助けたい訳じゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:25.34,Homura,,0,0,0,,I just don't want Madoka to witness your ruined appearance.{貴女が破滅していく姿を、まどかに見せたくないだけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:29.60,Homura,,0,0,0,,If you decline me here, you're just going to die anyway.{ここで私を拒むなら、どうせ貴女は死ぬしかない}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:32.64,Homura,,0,0,0,,If you're going to bring Madoka any further sorrow...{これ以上、まどかを悲しませるくらいなら}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.27,Homura,,0,0,0,,I would rather...{いっそ私が}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.27,Homura,,0,0,0,,...with this hand...{この手で}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.57,Homura,,0,0,0,,...kill you right now.{今すぐ殺してあげるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:41.03,Homura,,0,0,0,,Miki Sayaka.{美樹さやか}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.91,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Oi! Hurry up and escape!{オイ、さっさと逃げろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.21,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Are you insane?{正気かテメェは}{literal: Are you sane?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.30,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to help her?{アイツを助けるんじゃなかったのかよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:01.71,Homura,,0,0,0,,Let go.{離して}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.38,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,I get it.{なるほどね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:08.35,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,So if I'm holding on to you like this, it means you can't use that unusual technique?{こんな風にとっ捕まったままだと、あの妙な技も使えないってわけか}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:11.56,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Wha—{なっ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.24,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Damn it.{くそ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:33.79,Randoms,,0,0,0,,You can't let 'em make an excuse or anything.{言い訳とかさせちゃダメっしょー}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:36.83,Randoms,,0,0,0,,You need to keep close tabs on the full sum of their earned income.{稼いできた分は全額きっちり貢がせないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:43.09,Randoms,,0,0,0,,Women are idiots, after all. That's why if they possess even a little bit of wealth, they'll immediately use it on something worthless.{女って馬鹿だからさ。ちょっと金持たせとくとすっぐ下らねぇことに使っちまうからねぇ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:47.26,Randoms,,0,0,0,,Man, seriously. You can't treat women like humans, you know.{いや～ほんと 女は人間扱いしちゃ　ダメっすね～}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.80,Randoms,,0,0,0,,When you think of them as dogs or something, you have to discipline them, yeah.{犬かなんかだと思って　しつけないとね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.14,Randoms,,0,0,0,,She'll be delighted about that too.{アイツもそれで喜んでる訳だし}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:55.43,Randoms,,0,0,0,,If you say, "I'll punch you in the face!" then they'll almost always fall silent, man.{顔殴るぞって言えば、まず大抵は黙りますもんね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:14:00.52,Randoms,,0,0,0,,Pft. If you neglect them even a little bit, they'll instantly become spoiled and start saying stuff like they wanna "become family."{けっ、ちょっと油断すると、すぐつけあがって籍いれたいとかいいだすからさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.19,Randoms,,0,0,0,,It's a forbidden thing to pamper 'em.{甘やかすの禁物よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:07.07,Randoms,,0,0,0,,Man... In 10 years, a cabaret girl like {\i1}her{\i0} will be working for the same amount of money as she is now.{ったくテメーみてーなキャバ嬢が１０年後も同じ額稼げるかってーの}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:09.32,Randoms,,0,0,0,,She needs to understand her own limits, yeah?{身の程わきまえろってんだよ。なぁ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.24,Randoms,,0,0,0,,They're really annoying when you throw them away too, you know...{捨てる時もさぁホントウザいっすよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.08,Randoms,,0,0,0,,You're so skilled in that area, Shou-san, that it's enviable.{その辺ショウさん巧いから羨ましいっすよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.46,Randoms,,0,0,0,,I need to follow your example too—{俺も見習わないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.33,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Hey, let me hear more about that person.{ねえ、その人のこと、聞かせてよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.46,Randoms,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?{はい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:24.13,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,About the woman you guys were talking about just now...{今あんた達が話してた女の人のこと}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.21,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Let me hear more details.{もっとよく聞かせてよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.09,Randoms,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ojou-chan{\i0}, are you a middle school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.59,Randoms,,0,0,0,,It isn't good to be out playing at night.{夜遊びはよくないぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:36.23,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That person found you important, so she tried her best to please you, right?{その人、あんたの事が大事で、喜ばせたくて頑張ってたんでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.44,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,And you even understood that, right?{あんたにもそれが分かってたんでしょ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.23,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yet now she's the same as a dog?{なのに犬と同じなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.02,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You won't say thanks?{ありがとうって言わないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.48,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,She's useless now, so you'll throw her away?{役に立たなきゃ捨てちゃうの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.57,Randoms,,0,0,0,,What's with this person? Someone you know?{何こいつ？知り合い？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.40,Randoms,,0,0,0,,N–No...{い、いや}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:51.49,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Hey... does this world have value worth protecting?{ねえ、この世界って守る価値あるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.41,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,For what purpose was I fighting?{あたし何の為に戦ってたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.74,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Tell me.{教えてよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.12,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Right now. You tell me.{今すぐあんたが教えてよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:58.62,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'll...{でないとあたし…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:11.64,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan, where are you...{さやかちゃん…どこ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.44,QB,,0,0,0,,Do you resent me too, I wonder?{君も僕のことを恨んでいるのかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.82,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If I resented you, could that return Sayaka-chan to how she originally was?{あなたを恨んだら、さやかちゃんを元に戻してくれる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:30.57,QB,,0,0,0,,Impossible. My power is not extensive enough to do that.{無理だ。それは僕の力の及ぶことじゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:39.58,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Hey... that time, when you said that I "could become an amazing magical girl."{ねえ、いつか言ってた、私がすごい魔法少女になれるって話}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:41.87,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Was that... true?{あれは…本当なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.67,QB,,0,0,0,,Saying something like "amazing" is a humble way to put it.{凄いなんていうのは控えめな表現だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.55,QB,,0,0,0,,You'd become a ridiculous magical girl. {君は途方もない魔法少女になるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.34,QB,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the strongest in this world.{恐らくこの世界で最強の}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:54.85,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If I had accepted the task instead of Sayaka-chan, I wonder if she would've ended up becoming a magical girl.{私が引き受けてたら、さやかちゃんは魔法少女にならずに済んだのかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.97,QB,,0,0,0,,Sayaka achieved her own wish.{さやかは彼女の願いを遂げた}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.56,QB,,0,0,0,,Concerning that point, Madoka, you're not related at all.{その点について、まどかは何の関係もない}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.86,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Why is someone like me...{どうして私なんかが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.53,QB,,0,0,0,,I cannot comprehend that either.{僕にも分からない}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:11.70,QB,,0,0,0,,To say it clearly, the latent power hidden within yourself{はっきり言って君が秘めている潜在能力は、理論的にはあり得ない規模のものだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.61,QB,,0,0,0,,is on the scale of something that is theoretically impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:17.91,QB,,0,0,0,,Even I, too, want someone to explain it.{誰かに説明して欲しいのは、僕だって一緒さ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:18.62,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Is that so?{そうなの}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:22.66,QB,,0,0,0,,If the power within you were to be unlocked, creating a miracle would be nothing,{君が力を開放すれば、奇跡を起こすどころか }
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.50,QB,,0,0,0,,as I believe even distorting the laws of the universe would be possible.{宇宙の法則をねじ曲げることだって可能だろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:30.26,QB,,0,0,0,,Why are you the one single person who possesses characteristics to that extent?{なぜ君一人だけが、それほどの素質を備えているのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.76,QB,,0,0,0,,I do not yet understand the reason.{理由は未だにわからない}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.76,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I...{私は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:37.76,Madoka,,0,0,0,,thought of my lowly self as someone who had no redeeming qualities.{自分なんて何の取り柄もない人間だと思ってた}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:44.14,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I'd surely go on forever without benefiting or helping anyone else.{ずっとこのまま、誰のためになることも、何の役に立つこともできずに}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:47.90,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd simply be living for some reason or another until the end.{最後までただ何となく生きていくだけなのかなって}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:55.16,Madoka,,0,0,0,,That was something frustrating and lonely, but... I still thought, "It can't be helped." {それは悔しいし、寂しいことだけど、でも仕方ないよねって、思ってたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:59.91,QB,,0,0,0,,That's considerably different from reality, you know.{現実は随分と違ったね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:05.12,QB,,0,0,0,,Madoka, if you desire it, you may be able to become an omnipotent god.{まどか。君は、望むなら、万能の神にだってなれるかもしれないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.75,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If it's me...{私なら...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:11.92,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Kyubey, if it's me, I wonder if I could accomplish things that even you can't do.{キュゥべえにできないことでも、私ならできるのかな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.22,QB,,0,0,0,,So that means...?{というと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:17.34,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If I formed a contract with you, could I return Sayaka-chan's body back to its original state?{私があなたと契約したら、さやかちゃんの体を元に戻せる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.68,QB,,0,0,0,,I believe something of that level would surely be of no difficulty for you.{その程度、きっと造作もないだろうね}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:24.52,QB,,0,0,0,,In your eyes, is that wish something worth offering your soul for?{その願いは君にとって、魂を差し出すに足る物かい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.77,Madoka,,0,0,0,,If it's for Sayaka-chan's benefit, it's fine.{さやかちゃんのためなら…いいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.98,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I'll become a magical girl—{私、魔法少女に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.67,Madoka,,0,0,0,,A–Awful!{ひ…ひどいよ!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:51.34,Madoka,,0,0,0,,No matter what, you don't need to kill...{何も殺さなくても}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.30,Homura,,0,0,0,,You...{貴女は}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:57.93,Homura,,0,0,0,,Why do you always... sacrifice yourself like that?{なんで貴女は、いつだって、そうやって自分を犠牲にして}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.64,Homura,,0,0,0,,Saying things like you've never helped, or there's no point to you... {役に立たないとか、意味がないとか}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.56,Homura,,0,0,0,,Don't just decide you're inferior on your own...{勝手に自分を粗末にしないで}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:09.02,Homura,,0,0,0,,Think about the people who consider you precious too!{貴女を大切に思う人のことも考えて}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:10.65,Homura,,0,0,0,,I have had enough!{いい加減にしてよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:14.23,Homura,,0,0,0,,If you were lost, there are people who'd be sad...{貴女を失えば、それを悲しむ人がいるって}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.11,Homura,,0,0,0,,Why don't you realize that!?{どうしてそれに気づかないの！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.45,Homura,,0,0,0,,What will become of the people who protect you!?{貴女を守ろうとしてた人はどうなるの！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:24.75,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Homura-chan...{ほむらちゃん}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.75,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Have we, somewhere...{「私たちはどこかで…」 }
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:34.25,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Have we met somewhere before? With me...{どこかで会ったことあるの？私と}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:35.76,Homura,,0,0,0,,That is...{それは}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.64,Madoka,,0,0,0,,Sorry...{ごめん}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.27,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I have to search for Sayaka-chan.{私、さやかちゃんを探さないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:47.81,Homura,,0,0,0,,Wait...{まって}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.02,Homura,,0,0,0,,Miki Sayaka is already...{美樹さやかは、もう}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:51.86,Madoka,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.{ごめんね}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:54.61,Homura,,0,0,0,,Wait...{まって}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.15,Homura,,0,0,0,,Madoka!{まどか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.45,QB,,0,0,0,,Even though you know it's futile...{無駄な事だって知ってるくせに}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.45,QB,,0,0,0,,You just don't learn your lesson, do you?{懲りないんだなあ、君も}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:13.54,QB,,0,0,0,,There are as many replacements as necessary, but meaninglessly crushing one is still troubling, you know.{代わりはいくらでもあるけど、無意味に潰されるのは困るんだよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:14.75,QB,,0,0,0,,Isn't it wasteful?{勿体ないじゃないか}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.35,QB,,0,0,0,,This makes two times that you've killed me, but...{君に殺されたのは、これで二度目だけれど}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.98,QB,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, I can see the special characteristics of your attack.{おかげで攻撃の特性も見えてきた}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:38.24,QB,,0,0,0,,That was time-manipulation magic, right? Just before.{時間操作の魔術だろう？　さっきのは}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:41.86,QB,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.{やっぱりね}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.12,QB,,0,0,0,,Somehow I had a guess, but...{何となく察しはついてたけれど}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.74,QB,,0,0,0,,You're not a human being from this time axis, are you?{君はこの時間軸の人間じゃないね}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:53.29,Homura,,0,0,0,,Your true character and your plan... I know everything.{お前のも企みも、私は全て知ってるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.63,QB,,0,0,0,,I see.{なるほどね}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.96,QB,,0,0,0,,That's the reason why you've been going so far to get in my way.{だからこんなにしつこく僕の邪魔をするわけだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:00.76,QB,,0,0,0,,You would go that far for your desire to change Kaname Madoka's fate?{そうまでして、鹿目まどかの運命を変えたいのかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:01.68,Homura,,0,0,0,,Yes.{ええ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:06.43,Homura,,0,0,0,,I absolutely will not allow things to go according to your plan.{絶対にお前の思い通りにはさせない}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:06.76,Homura,,0,0,0,,Kyubey.{QB}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.89,Homura,,0,0,0,,No... Incubator.{いいえ、インキュベーター}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.07,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Finally found you...{やっと見つけた…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:29.49,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Hey you, how long are you going to keep being stubborn?{アンタさ、いつまで強情張ってるわけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:33.92,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I took away your time.{悪いね、手間かけさせちゃって}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:34.62,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,What's that?{何だよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.96,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,This isn't like you, is it?{らしくないじゃんかよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:37.54,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{うん}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:42.22,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That's because I don't particularly care anymore, you know.{別にもう、どうでも良くなっちゃったからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:47.85,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,In the end, I... Just what exactly did I find precious, and what was I protecting? {結局私は、一体何が大切で何を守ろうとしてたのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:51.60,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all has any reason anymore.{もう何もかも、わけ分かんなくなっちゃった }
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.10,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Oi...{おい}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:21:00.61,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,"Hope and despair balance out to reach equilibrium and become zero..."{希望と絶望のバランスは差し引きゼロだって}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:03.11,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,There was one time, right? That you said that.{いつだったかあんた言ってたよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:06.11,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,If it's now, I understand that very well.{今ならそれ、よく分かるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:11.24,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I certainly did save some number of people, but...{確かに私は何人か救いもしたけどさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:15.62,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,But, in proportion to that, resentment and jealousy accumulated in my heart.{だけどその分、心には恨みや妬みが溜まって}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:19.00,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I even hurt my most precious friend's feelings.{一番大切な友達さえ傷付けて}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:21.46,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Sayaka! You couldn't be...!{さやか、アンタまさか}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:26.38,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,To counteract a prayer for someone's happiness, someone else has to be cursed.{誰かの幸せを祈った分、他の誰かを呪わずにはいられない}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:31.01,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,We magical girls are structured in that kind of way, aren't we?{私達魔法少女って、そう言う仕組みだったんだね}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.11,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'm...{\alpha&HFF&} really an idiot.{あたしって、ホントばか}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:40.07,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I'm... really an idiot.{あたしって、ホントばか}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:05.67,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Sayaka!!!{さやかぁぁっ！！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:15.89,QB,,0,0,0,,In this country, women in the middle of growing to adulthood are called "girls," right?{この国では、成長途中の女性のことを、少女って呼ぶんだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:20.53,QB,,0,0,0,,Well then, for those of you who will become witches before long...{だったら、やがて魔女になる君たちのことは}
