Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:23:59.50,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you think I'm an idiot, but...{バカと思うかもしれないけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.50,0:24:03.12,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,As for me, y'know... Whether or not she can really be saved...{アタシはね。本当に助けられないのかどうか}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:05.71,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,Until we ascertain that, I don't want to give up.{それを確かめるまで、諦めたくない}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:09.51,Kyouko,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't forgive that sort of thing.{そんなのアタシが許さない}
